<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>爬虫管理后台</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    
    .container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      color: white;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    
    .header h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    }
    
    .header p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }
    
    .crawler-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 30px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    
    .crawler-section {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 30px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
    }
    
    .section-title {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      padding-bottom: 15px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #f0f0f0;
    }
    
    .section-title span {
      width: 10px;
      height: 30px;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    
    .section-title.us span {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #4CAF50, #45a049);
    }
    
    .section-title.cn span {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f44336, #da190b);
    }
    
    .section-title h2 {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      color: #333;
    }
    
    .section-title .subtitle {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: #999;
      font-weight: normal;
      margin-left: auto;
    }
    
    .btn-grid {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    
    .btn {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 16px 24px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 10px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: white;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .btn::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: -100%;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.2), transparent);
      transition: left 0.5s ease;
    }
    
    .btn:hover::before {
      left: 100%;
    }
    
    .btn-us {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4CAF50, #45a049);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.3);
    }
    
    .btn-us:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.4);
    }
    
    .btn-cn {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f44336, #da190b);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(244, 67, 54, 0.3);
    }
    
    .btn-cn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(244, 67, 54, 0.4);
    }
    
    .btn:active {
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
    
    .btn i {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }
    
    .results-section {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 30px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
    }
    
    .results-title {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    
    .results-title h2 {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      color: #333;
    }
    
    .results-list {
      max-height: 400px;
      overflow-y: auto;
    }
    
    .result-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 15px;
      padding: 15px 20px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: #f8f9fa;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    .result-item:hover {
      background: #e9ecef;
    }
    
    .result-status {
      width: 12px;
      height: 12px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    
    .result-status.success {
      background: #4CAF50;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.5);
    }
    
    .result-status.error {
      background: #f44336;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(244, 67, 54, 0.5);
    }
    
    .result-content {
      flex: 1;
    }
    
    .result-task {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #333;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    
    .result-message {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #666;
    }
    
    .result-meta {
      text-align: right;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: #999;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    
    .empty-state {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 40px;
      color: #999;
    }
    
    .empty-state i {
      font-size: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      opacity: 0.5;
    }
    
    .empty-state p {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
    
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      color: white;
      margin-top: 30px;
      opacity: 0.8;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
    
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .crawler-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
      
      .header h1 {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>📊 爬虫管理后台</h1>
      <p>内部测试/运维专用 - 免登录访问</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="crawler-grid">
      <div class="crawler-section">
        <div class="section-title us">
          <span></span>
          <h2>🇺🇸 美股爬虫区</h2>
          <span class="subtitle">3个任务</span>
        </div>
        <div class="btn-grid">
          <a href="/admin/stock_crawlers/us_stock_list" class="btn btn-us">
            <span>📋</span>
            <span>爬取美股列表</span>
          </a>
          <a href="/admin/stock_crawlers/us_stock_basic" class="btn btn-us">
            <span>🏢</span>
            <span>爬取美股名称&行业</span>
          </a>
          <a href="/admin/stock_crawlers/us_finance" class="btn btn-us">
            <span>💰</span>
            <span>爬取美股全套财务</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="crawler-section">
        <div class="section-title cn">
          <span></span>
          <h2>🇨🇳 A股爬虫区</h2>
          <span class="subtitle">2个任务</span>
        </div>
        <div class="btn-grid">
          <a href="/admin/stock_crawlers/a_stock_list" class="btn btn-cn">
            <span>📋</span>
            <span>爬取A股列表、名称&行业</span>
          </a>
          <a href="/admin/stock_crawlers/a_finance" class="btn btn-cn">
            <span>💰</span>
            <span>爬取A股全套财务</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="results-section">
      <div class="results-title">
        <h2>📝 执行结果</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="results-list">
        <% if @results.present? %>
          <% @results.each do |result| %>
            <div class="result-item">
              <div class="result-status <%= result[:status] %>"></div>
              <div class="result-content">
                <div class="result-task"><%= result[:task_name] %></div>
                <div class="result-message"><%= result[:message] %></div>
              </div>
              <div class="result-meta">
                <div><%= result[:executed_at] %></div>
                <div>耗时: <%= result[:duration] %>s</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        <% else %>
          <div class="empty-state">
            <span>🔄</span>
            <p>暂无执行记录，请点击上方按钮开始爬取任务</p>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>⚠️ 注意：任务执行期间请耐心等待，请勿重复点击</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>